TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action (Alternate)
TriggerLogic.CodeStr:
local units = GG.mission.FindUnitsInGroup("Berthas") for unitID in pairs(units) do local x, y, z = Spring.GetUnitPosition(unitID) Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, CMD.ATTACK, {x, y, z - 5000}, 0) end
local units2 = GG.mission.FindUnitsInGroup("Planes") for unitID in pairs(units2) do local x, y, z = Spring.GetUnitPosition(unitID) local z2 = z - 10000 local y2 = Spring.GetGroundHeight(x, z2) Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, CMD.FIGHT, {x, y2, z2}, {}) end
